### Get all articles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Accept: application/hal+json

### Get specific article
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1
Accept: application/hal+json

### Create new article
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Article from HTTP Client",
  "content": "This article was created using IntelliJ HTTP Client",
  "author": "Developer"
}

### Update article (replace {id} with actual article id)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Article",
  "content": "Updated content",
  "publishedDate": "2025-10-02T10:00:00",
  "author": "Updated Author"
}

### Delete article (replace {id} with actual article id)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1

### Get Atom feed
GET http://localhost:8080/feed/atom
Accept: application/atom+xml

### Get RSS feed
GET http://localhost:8080/feed/rss
Accept: application/rss+xml

### Examples with Basic Authentication (when enabled)

### Get articles with auth
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Accept: application/hal+json
Authorization: Basic user password

### Create article with auth
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic admin admin

{
  "title": "Authenticated Article",
  "content": "Created with authentication",
  "author": "Admin User"
}
